title: DPS-BEST OF- Sep 11, 2020
itunes:title: DPS-BEST OF- Sep 11, 2020
description:
On Today's Episode of the Dan Patrick Show, we recap the NFL season's opening game between the Chiefs and Texans. We've got a nickname for Rookie Running Back Clyde Edwards Helaire. We're joined by Houston area radio host Sean Salisbury, ESPN's Chris Fowler and legendary broadcaster Vin Scully. Plus, DP has some words for Dak Prescott, who recently revealed he's dealt with depression.
